NK005(ca)001:0: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba zhes bya ba rgyud kyi rgyal po bzhugs so //
NK005(ca)001:2: sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga tan+t+ra r+aa dza n+aa ma /
NK005(ca)001:4: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba zhes bya ba rgyud kyi rgyal po /
NK005(ca)001:5: bcom ldan 'das ye shes dbugs 'byin gyi rgyal po
NK005(ca)001:6: shin tu rnam par grol ba nyid la phyag 'tshal
NK005(ca)001:7: lo // 'di skad bdag gis go ba nyid kyi thos pa'i dus na /
NK005(ca)001:8: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'dus pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)001:9: sna tshogs snang ba gcig pu nyid //
NK005(ca)001:11: gcig pu rab tu che ba'i lha //
NK005(ca)001:12: rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba'i 'od //
NK005(ca)001:14: brjid mdangs gzi chen rab tu che //
NK005(ca)001:15: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba'i mchog /
NK005(ca)001:16: dpal ldan dgyes pa ye shes sku //
NK005(ca)001:17: ngo bo nyid las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK005(ca)001:18: gcig ni kun tu snang ba de //
NK005(ca)001:19: sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK005(ca)001:20: so sor rang rig 'dus pa'i dpal //
NK005(ca)001:21: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang sku //
NK005(ca)001:22: yon tan phrin las phyogs dus kun //
NK005(ca)001:23: ma lus mi lus lus med gnas //
NK005(ca)001:24: 'og min rang byung chos kyi dbyings //
NK005(ca)001:25: gsang ba mchog gi dgyes pa na //
NK005(ca)001:26: dus gsum bdag po rdo rje 'chang //
NK005(ca)001:27: rnam par thar pa'i dbu mnga' zhing //
NK005(ca)001:28: pha rol phyin drug phyag rgya 'bar //
NK005(ca)001:29: brtul zhugs mnyam nyid skyil mo krung //
NK005(ca)001:30: ye shes sku ni zang thal zhal //
NK005(ca)001:31: gti mug gdung dang zhe sdang gdung //
NK005(ca)001:32: shin tu gdug pa 'dul ba'i gdung //
NK005(ca)001:33: ser sna'i gdung dang 'dod chags gdung //
NK005(ca)001:34: phrag dog gdung dang shin tu spro //
NK005(ca)001:35: sprin phung 'khrigs pa'i dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)001:36: thams cad bdag nyid rtag tu bzhugs //
NK005(ca)001:37: yang dag bsgrub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK005(ca)001:38: sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus pa //
NK005(ca)001:39: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog bde //
NK005(ca)001:40: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)001:41: rnal 'byor zab mo sku gsum rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:42: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK005(ca)001:43: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK005(ca)001:44: dga' dang mchog dga' dga' ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:45: lhan cig skyes dag'i rang bzhin can //
NK005(ca)001:46: sgyu ma chen po chos kyi sku //
NK005(ca)001:47: gsang ba shes rab bde chen po //
NK005(ca)001:48: bstan par bzhed nas dkyil 'khor spro //
NK005(ca)001:49: stong pa ye shes rab snang ba //
NK005(ca)001:50: tshogs pa'i dus na rnam par dag /
NK005(ca)001:51: de nas nyid kyi bde 'byin mas //
NK005(ca)001:52: klu yi rnam par bskul mdzad do //
NK005(ca)001:53: mi 'da' stong nyid gar gyi bdag /
NK005(ca)001:54: g.yar dam snying po dngos grub mdzod //
NK005(ca)001:55: dam tshig chen po ngo bo nyid //
NK005(ca)001:56: ye shes can du grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)001:57: hoh e ma ngo mtshar ya mtshan can //
NK005(ca)001:58: rig pa'i rnam pa stong nyid thugs //
NK005(ca)001:59: ye shes rol pa rnam par rol //
NK005(ca)001:60: rol pa'i ngang nas dam tshig 'byin //
NK005(ca)001:61: pad+ma rgyas par gar mdzad de //
NK005(ca)001:62: rig pa nyid du mjal bar byed //
NK005(ca)001:63: ces de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du gleng ngo //
NK005(ca)001:64: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:65: rgyud 'byung ba'i gzhi rnam par bkod pa ste rtog pa dang po'o //
NK005(ca)001:67: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang
NK005(ca)001:68: ba bka' bgros pa zhes bya ba'i sprul pa rnam
NK005(ca)001:69: par phyung ste 'dul bar dgongs nas /
NK005(ca)001:70: thugs rjes spro ba 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:71: rig pa nyid las skyes pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)001:72: sku gsum yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK005(ca)001:73: rig pa shes pa rnam drug che //
NK005(ca)001:74: chos nyid ngang du ye shes gnas //
NK005(ca)001:75: mi skye'i chos can skye tshul ston //
NK005(ca)001:76: thabs dang shes rab mnyam sbyor mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:77: dug lnga ye shes lnga yis 'joms //
NK005(ca)001:78: ci yang mi gsung mnyam par gnas //
NK005(ca)001:80: dbyings la ye shes rol rtsed mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:81: nam mkha' lta bur sna tshogs ston //
NK005(ca)001:82: bdud rtsi dam pa'i chu bo 'bebs //
NK005(ca)001:83: ma rig sel ba'i sgron me mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:84: 'khor ba'i nang nas byung tshul ston //
NK005(ca)001:85: rdo rje'i gdan la rdo rje 'jog /
NK005(ca)001:86: bye ba khrag khrig gdul bya la //
NK005(ca)001:87: de dang mthun par sprul pa 'gyed //
NK005(ca)001:88: dpa' bor mos la dpa' bo dang //
NK005(ca)001:89: dpa' mor mos la dpa' mo dang //
NK005(ca)001:90: mthun byas mthun pas don mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)001:94: de nas gdul bya 'dul dka' ba dag dbugs dbyung ba'i phyir /
NK005(ca)001:95: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK005(ca)001:96: dgongs pa dam pa gsang ba bkod pa zhes bya
NK005(ca)001:97: ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas 'di
NK005(ca)001:98: gsungs so // mthun byas sku yi don mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)001:99: rigs drug dam tshig las sbyang phyir //
NK005(ca)001:100: ye shes ngang las dam tshig chen pos bskul //
NK005(ca)001:101: bde gshegs thams cad rnam par bka' bgros mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:102: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis rdo rje zhe sdang chen po la bskul ba /
NK005(ca)001:103: rjes su chags pa rnam mang pad+mo rnam dag pa /
NK005(ca)001:104: mchod pa gsal bar rjes su mchod byas nas /
NK005(ca)001:105: mchog tu rtag pa'i rnal 'byor bde bas bde ba grub par mdzod /
NK005(ca)001:107: mchog tu bde ba'i rnal 'byor shin tu skal bzang mchog mnyes pa /
NK005(ca)001:108: rang gi dam tshig skyon med par rol cig /
NK005(ca)001:109: hohe ma hoh bde mchog bde drongs rnam par sprul //
NK005(ca)001:110: dzahmh'u bam hohh+aum gnang bar mdzod /
NK005(ca)001:111: a la la hoh de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK005(ca)001:112: rnams kyis 'khor gti mug chen po la bskul ba
NK005(ca)001:113: e ma hoh mchog tu gsang ba'i dam tshig yin
NK005(ca)001:114: pa'i phyir / rab tu gsang ba'i lha mo mchog rnams so //
NK005(ca)001:115: 'gro ba'i rgyun ni rnam pa sna tshogs 'dul ba rab gsal mkhyen /
NK005(ca)001:116: dam tshig thams cad dngos po'i brtan g.yo kun gyi ngo bor 'gyur /
NK005(ca)001:117: rgyal ba kun gyi bdag nyid rnal 'byor bde ba'i
NK005(ca)001:118: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma rnam sprul hoh kye ma dam
NK005(ca)001:119: pa rtag pa'i dngos grub chen po rab tu bsgrub
NK005(ca)001:120: pa ston / e ma hoh bde mchog bde drongs rnam par sprul //
NK005(ca)001:121: h'u rnam par snang mdzad a la la hoh dzahh+aum
NK005(ca)001:122: bam hoh de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis
NK005(ca)001:123: shin tu khro gtum gdug pa chen po la bskul
NK005(ca)001:124: ba / rnam pa mang po khro bo'i rgyud kyis sems can ma lus pa //
NK005(ca)001:125: lus pa med pa thugs rje'i thugs kyis 'dul mkhas pa //
NK005(ca)001:126: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma yi //
NK005(ca)001:127: bde mchog sgyu ma thams cad rnam sprul rnam par sprul //
NK005(ca)001:128: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:129: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis rin chen ser sna chen po la bskul ba /
NK005(ca)001:130: rnam pa mang po rab tu dga' ba'i rgyud kyi sems can la //
NK005(ca)001:131: ma lus lus pa med par 'dul mkhas pa //
NK005(ca)001:132: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma la //
NK005(ca)001:133: sgyu ma bde mchog sgyu mas rnam sprul rnam par sprul /
NK005(ca)001:135: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis pad+ma 'dod chags chen po la bskul ba /
NK005(ca)001:136: rnam pa mang po 'dod chags rgyud kyi sems can la //
NK005(ca)001:137: ma lus lus pa med pas 'dul mkhas pa'i //
NK005(ca)001:138: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma yi //
NK005(ca)001:139: bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rnam par sprul //
NK005(ca)001:141: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis phrag dog rgya gram chen po la bskul ba /
NK005(ca)001:142: rnam pa mang pos srog gi rgyud kyis sems can la //
NK005(ca)001:143: ma lus lus pa med pa 'dul mkhas pa //
NK005(ca)001:144: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma yi //
NK005(ca)001:145: bde mchog sgyu mas rnam sprul rnam par sprul //
NK005(ca)001:146: h'u bi shwa bi sh+ya h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:147: de nas bcom ldan 'das 'gro drug sbyong ba'i rgyal po rnams sku rnam par sprul cing phyung ba /
NK005(ca)001:148: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:149: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:150: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK005(ca)001:151: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:152: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK005(ca)001:153: mngon par zhen cing ltung bar gyur //
NK005(ca)001:154: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam sprul gyis //
NK005(ca)001:155: cho ga sna tshogs 'dod rnams la //
NK005(ca)001:156: las kyi sbyor ba sna tshogs kyis //
NK005(ca)001:157: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin la sogs //
NK005(ca)001:158: 'dul ba'i phyir na sprul pa yin //
NK005(ca)001:159: sangs rgyas la sogs brtan g.yo ku //
NK005(ca)001:161: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)001:162: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK005(ca)001:163: sgyu ma sbyor ba 'di yis ni //
NK005(ca)001:164: rnam pa sna tshogs kun gyi mchog /
NK005(ca)001:165: sems can kun gyi don mchog rnams //
NK005(ca)001:167: ces dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:168: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:169: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:170: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK005(ca)001:171: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:172: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK005(ca)001:173: shin tu stong pa nyid la brtson //
NK005(ca)001:174: 'gog pa'i chos nyid la sbyor bas //
NK005(ca)001:177: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK005(ca)001:178: 'gro ba thams cad rnam sbyang phyir //
NK005(ca)001:179: sangs rgyas sprul pa kun tu 'gyed //
NK005(ca)001:180: stong pa ma yin mi stong min //
NK005(ca)001:181: dbu mar yang ni mi dmigs te //
NK005(ca)001:182: shes rab pha rol phyin sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)001:183: thabs kyi snying rje'i bdag nyid rnams //
NK005(ca)001:184: de bas de ni snying rje'i thabs //
NK005(ca)001:185: shes rab pha rol phyin par gsal //
NK005(ca)001:186: rtog pa med pa'i chos rnams las //
NK005(ca)001:187: sems can don du yang rtog pa //
NK005(ca)001:188: rnam par mi rtog la mos pas //
NK005(ca)001:189: thams cad rtog pas rtag par bya //
NK005(ca)001:190: zhes rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:191: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:192: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:193: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK005(ca)001:194: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:195: de tshe sems can thams cad kun //
NK005(ca)001:196: shin tu khro gtum gdug par gyur //
NK005(ca)001:197: shin tu gdug cing khros pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:199: shin tu gdug cig khro ba la //
NK005(ca)001:200: zhi bas phan pas mi 'gyur te //
NK005(ca)001:201: shes rab thabs kyi rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:202: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:203: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
NK005(ca)001:204: 'jig rten gsum dag bsreg byed na //
NK005(ca)001:205: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:206: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
NK005(ca)001:207: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK005(ca)001:208: dam tshig la sdang rnam sbyang phyir //
NK005(ca)001:209: dur khrod gar gyi phyag rgya gsal //
NK005(ca)001:210: thar pa nag po dregs ldan dang //
NK005(ca)001:211: tshangs chen 'jug sel lha chen dang //
NK005(ca)001:212: gu lang dbang chen nye dbang bcas //
NK005(ca)001:213: nyi zla gshin rje tshangs pa rnams //
NK005(ca)001:214: bsgral nas thal ba rdul du bshig /
NK005(ca)001:215: rdo rje kha t+w+aam dril gsil shing //
NK005(ca)001:216: thal bar gyur pa 'tsho bar byas //
NK005(ca)001:217: sems can khams ni rnam sbyangs nas //
NK005(ca)001:218: dag pa'i sangs rgyas zhing rnams su //
NK005(ca)001:219: sangs rgyas byang chub dag la bkod //
NK005(ca)001:220: rdo rje 'dod khro la sogs kyi //
NK005(ca)001:221: rtog pa bla med thams cad ni //
NK005(ca)001:222: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mkha' klas pa'i //
NK005(ca)001:223: sems can khams ni rnam par sbyangs //
NK005(ca)001:224: zhes he ru kas dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:225: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:226: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yi //
NK005(ca)001:227: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK005(ca)001:228: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:229: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK005(ca)001:230: log par blta la gnas par gyur //
NK005(ca)001:231: lta ba shin tu ngan pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:234: byang chub sems ni rnam sbyang phyir //
NK005(ca)001:235: chags pa'i pad+mo rdo rje chos //
NK005(ca)001:236: he ru kar gnas nyes skyon bral //
NK005(ca)001:237: khams gsum nyes sbyangs spyan ras gzigs //
NK005(ca)001:238: pad+ma gar dbang phyag rgyar gsal //
NK005(ca)001:239: 'dod chags thams cad dag pa na //
NK005(ca)001:241: 'dul bar gsal bas don la sbyor //
NK005(ca)001:242: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gis //
NK005(ca)001:243: nam mkha'i mtha' klas rtog pa rnams //
NK005(ca)001:244: sems can khams rnams sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)001:245: chags pa'i don gyis rnam par sbyang //
NK005(ca)001:246: zhes pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug gis dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:247: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:248: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yi //
NK005(ca)001:249: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK005(ca)001:250: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:251: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK005(ca)001:252: shin tu gdug cig brkam par gyur //
NK005(ca)001:253: brdungs shing brkam pas yi dwags ltung //
NK005(ca)001:254: de nas 'phos nas dbul por skyes //
NK005(ca)001:255: de yi skyon gyis gsod par byed //
NK005(ca)001:256: shin tu gdug pa sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)001:258: dam pa'i don chen nyi ma byung //
NK005(ca)001:259: nam mkha'i snying po'i rin chen gyi //
NK005(ca)001:260: re ba kun yang yongs rdzogs mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:261: khro gtum zhi bas mi 'dul phyir //
NK005(ca)001:262: shes rab thabs kyi rnal 'byor pa //
NK005(ca)001:263: rdo rje nyi ma'i phyag rgyar gsal //
NK005(ca)001:264: 'jig rten gsum sogs rtog pa kun //
NK005(ca)001:265: sbyangs nas yon tan rgyas shing 'phel //
NK005(ca)001:266: rdo rje nyi mas dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:267: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:268: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa yi //
NK005(ca)001:269: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK005(ca)001:270: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:271: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK005(ca)001:272: brtson 'grus shin tu chung bar gyur //
NK005(ca)001:273: shin tu brtson 'grus chung ba yis //
NK005(ca)001:274: mnar med pa yi dmyal bar ltung //
NK005(ca)001:276: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK005(ca)001:277: drag shul sbyor ba'i tshul dag tu //
NK005(ca)001:278: rta mchog dpal du rnam par snang //
NK005(ca)001:279: shin tu khro zhing gtum pa la //
NK005(ca)001:280: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK005(ca)001:281: khro bo de bzhin gshegs pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:282: sdig med stobs kyis ngo mthon du //
NK005(ca)001:283: dregs pa pho ni mnan nas su //
NK005(ca)001:284: de tshe yum rnams rang gis spyad //
NK005(ca)001:285: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub kyis //
NK005(ca)001:286: rta mchog rnam par 'phrul pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:287: ma lus lus pa med pa yi //
NK005(ca)001:288: sems can rnams kyi don yang byed //
NK005(ca)001:289: rta mchog dpal gyi rgyal po yis //
NK005(ca)001:290: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mtha' don bsgrubs //
NK005(ca)001:291: zhes dpal rta mchog gis dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:292: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:293: rigs drug gi 'gro ba la sprul pa rol pa'i
NK005(ca)001:294: lo rgyus bkod pas rtog pa ste le'u gnyis pa'o
NK005(ca)001:296: // // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung
NK005(ca)001:297: rnam par rol pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK005(ca)001:299: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las 'dus pa las 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK005(ca)001:300: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)001:301: d+harma d+h+aa tu badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)001:302: h+aum tsit+ta pra be s+pha ra na phata /
NK005(ca)001:306: su ru me sum lam tish+tha man+da la /
NK005(ca)001:308: rak+ta m+aam sa kem ram b+h+r+aum tsakra man+da la /
NK005(ca)001:312: b+h+r+aum badz+ra bi shwa man+da la /
NK005(ca)001:330: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sat+wa a dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK005(ca)001:331: su ra ta s+t+wam dza badz+ra drish+ti swa ye ka
NK005(ca)001:332: mat+ta / h+aum badz+ra k+ai li k+ai li h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:333: bam badz+ri nirma ra ra ta hoh badz+ra k+aa le shwa ri tri /
NK005(ca)001:335: +amo badz+ra me g+ha ga g+hu lu g+hu lu b+h+r+aum /
NK005(ca)001:336: +amo ha sha rasta badz+re ni i i /
NK005(ca)001:337: kham badz+ra shi shi ri h+aum h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:338: +amo b+hu kham badz+ra sa ra sham /
NK005(ca)001:342: ham sarba badz+ra tshe badz+ra ta tre /
NK005(ca)001:345: +amo he ru ka badz+ra sa ma y+aa hi /
NK005(ca)001:346: sarba dush+ta sa ma ya mu dra pra b+hany+dza ka h'u phata /
NK005(ca)001:347: +amo badz+ra gu h+ya sid+d+hi pa ra ma yo g+ai shwa ri h+r+ai h'u h'u /
NK005(ca)001:348: badz+ra tsam re sh+aa ri kha dam gi ma hi /
NK005(ca)001:349: badz+ra ka pa l+aa ma ku di ru lu ru lu hi na /
NK005(ca)001:350: h'u badz+ra na da ya ni dza dz+hi /
NK005(ca)001:351: +amo badz+ra sa t+wa ke dzi h'u badz+ra pra ha ra na ma d+ha /
NK005(ca)001:352: am badz+ra shu l+ai gra b+hi b+ha h'u phata /
NK005(ca)001:353: h'u badz+ra yo she tsin+d+ha ma da /
NK005(ca)001:354: h'u badz+ra me la da she ma da /
NK005(ca)001:356: pa ma h+aa ra ti badz+ri he /
NK005(ca)001:358: ram ma h+aa shwi badz+ra hi /
NK005(ca)001:359: si d+h+ya b+hu si d+h+ya b+ha ba si d+h+ya /
NK005(ca)001:360: ma h+aa badz+ra rat+na ba ba da da ram /
NK005(ca)001:361: badz+ra sa t+wa dzah badz+ra rat+na h'u /
NK005(ca)001:363: badz+ra karma hoh pri ti badz+ra ni ma da sa /
NK005(ca)001:364: badz+ra pri ti hrih badz+ra tsi tra ma ni hoh badz+ra ma h+aa ma ho h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:365: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha pad+ma na te ba sha h+r+aih sarba ta ka g+aa ra pad+ma dza h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:368: ho pad+ma ni ra dzah h'u pad+ma tsam de shwa ri h'u phata /
NK005(ca)001:369: he ma h+aa bi shwa pad+ma mu te sid+d+hi h'u phata /
NK005(ca)001:371: ho pad+mi bi shwa kri ma kra ma h+aum dza /
NK005(ca)001:374: bi shwa badz+ra sa t+wa ha /
NK005(ca)001:375: he ra ti badz+ra bi l+aa si ni dra da /
NK005(ca)001:376: he ra ti badz+ra gi te te te te /
NK005(ca)001:377: he ra ti badz+ra h+aa se ha ha bam /
NK005(ca)001:378: he ri ti badz+ra n+ri t+ye pi ba be ba d+ha /
NK005(ca)001:384: +amo ha ya g+r+ai ba spush+ti h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:388: +amo hu lu g+r+ai ba ba sham h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:393: am e ma ra hu lu h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:394: +amo badz+ra am ku sha dzah +amo badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:399: ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi hu /
NK005(ca)001:400: sarba sid+d+hi hu sa ma yo ta mu /
NK005(ca)001:401: ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi hu /
NK005(ca)001:402: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsungs pas /
NK005(ca)001:403: stong gsum thams cad skus gang /
NK005(ca)001:406: de nas de bzhin gshegs pas thams cad kyi sku'i snying po zhes bya ba 'di phyung ngo //
NK005(ca)001:407: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa
NK005(ca)001:408: tu +aah zhes gsungs pa'i zhi ba'i tshogs thams cad
NK005(ca)001:410: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung gi snying po 'di phyung ngo //
NK005(ca)001:412: ces gsungs pas gsung gi tshogs thams cad dgyes par gyur to //
NK005(ca)001:413: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi snying po 'di phyung ngo //
NK005(ca)001:414: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:415: zhes gsungs pas khro bo'i tshogs thams cad dgyes par gyur to //
NK005(ca)001:416: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yon tan gyi snying po 'di phyung ngo //
NK005(ca)001:417: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK005(ca)001:418: zhes gsungs pas yon tan gyis rab tu gang ngo //
NK005(ca)001:419: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi phrin las kyi snying po 'di phyung ngo //
NK005(ca)001:422: grih+na pa ya grih+na pa ya h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:423: +aa na ya hoh b+ha ga w+aan /
NK005(ca)001:425: ces gsungs pas phrin las yongs su grub bo //
NK005(ca)001:426: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis yongs su gsang ba zhes bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:427: dzahh+aum bam hoh e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan /
NK005(ca)001:428: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka /
NK005(ca)001:429: dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)001:430: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsha ya tish+tha lhan /
NK005(ca)001:431: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK005(ca)001:432: pra na me na badz+ra ban+d+ha nam ka ro mi
NK005(ca)001:436: ma h+aa shu nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)001:437: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+ri ye h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:438: sarba ta th+aa ga ta u ga ta a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK005(ca)001:439: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya b+aa ka tsit+ta h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:440: e +aa ra li hrimh dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra d+aak+ki
NK005(ca)001:441: ni sa ma ya ham dri sh+ya hoh badz+ra d+aak+ki
NK005(ca)001:442: ni i dam ba lim grih+nan+tu sa ma ya rak+shan+tu
NK005(ca)001:443: / bud+d+ha d+aak+ki mi i dam ba lim grih+nan+tu sa ma ya rak+shan+tu /
NK005(ca)001:444: rat+na d+aak+ki ni i dam ba lim grih+nan+tu sa ma ya rak+shan+tu /
NK005(ca)001:446: to sha ya to sha ya /
NK005(ca)001:448: sarba d+aak+ki ni e +aa ral+li h+r+aih pad+ma d+aa k+ki
NK005(ca)001:449: ni i dam ba lim grih+nan+tu sa ma ya rak+shan+tu
NK005(ca)001:450: / karma d+aak+ki ni i dam ba lim grih+nan+tu sa ma ya rak+shan+tu /
NK005(ca)001:451: sarba d+aak+ki ni i dam ba lim grih+nan+tu sa ma ya rak+shan+tu /
NK005(ca)001:452: sh+ma sha na d+aak+ki ni i dam ba lim grih+nan+tu sa ma ya rak+shan+ta /
NK005(ca)001:453: zhes gsungs pas thams cad mnyes par gyur to //
NK005(ca)001:454: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:455: gsung gi 'khor lo'i rtog pa ste le'u gsum pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:457: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:458: sangs rgyas 'di tshe bsgrub bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)001:459: sku gsum pa la goms par bya //
NK005(ca)001:460: dang po chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK005(ca)001:461: dmigs pa med pa'i don gyis bsgom //
NK005(ca)001:462: bsgrub med yum gyi b+ha ga la //
NK005(ca)001:463: brjod med sems kyi ngang du gsal //
NK005(ca)001:464: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NK005(ca)001:465: thams cad kun la khyab par bya //
NK005(ca)001:466: rtsol med ma bsgrubs ji ltar las //
NK005(ca)001:467: kun snang nam mkha'i ngang nyid 'byung //
NK005(ca)001:468: med pa'i rgyu las mngon gsal ba //
NK005(ca)001:469: sems kyi rang bzhin ye shes gsal //
NK005(ca)001:470: dam pa'i yi ge las ni //
NK005(ca)001:471: ye shes sems dpa' gsal bar shar //
NK005(ca)001:472: 'byung lnga'i dam pa rin chen dbyings //
NK005(ca)001:473: stong gsal g.yo zhing sdud pa'i chu //
NK005(ca)001:474: sra mkhregs sreg byed 'bar ba'i me //
NK005(ca)001:477: bzhugs gnas 'bar ba chos kyi dbyings //
NK005(ca)001:478: ye shes drug gi gzhal yas khang //
NK005(ca)001:479: rang gnas mdzes pa'i dbyings dang ldan //
NK005(ca)001:480: h+aum 'bar sgeg pa'i nyams can zhal //
NK005(ca)001:481: rdo rje kha t+w+aam dril bu 'khrol //
NK005(ca)001:482: thabs dang shes rab mda' gzhu 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:483: mthing ga mtshan dang dpe byad rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:484: bde mchog dkar mo dzahls skyes //
NK005(ca)001:485: thabs dang shes rab mda' gzhu 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:486: h+aum skyes gser mdog e ma bde //
NK005(ca)001:489: snang mdzad dmar po rdo rje thod //
NK005(ca)001:490: thabs kyi kha t+w+aam rab tu 'khrol //
NK005(ca)001:491: ho skyes ljang gu slob ma mo //
NK005(ca)001:492: 'khyud cing bdud rtsi rab tu gsol //
NK005(ca)001:493: shar phyogs rim bzhin byang du 'khod //
NK005(ca)001:495: / sangs rgyas byang chub dkar mo che //
NK005(ca)001:496: dus gcig tshangs mgo mda' gzhu 'phen //
NK005(ca)001:498: chos kyi 'khor lo dkar ser ma //
NK005(ca)001:499: dmar skya rnam rgyal ha las byung //
NK005(ca)001:500: tri sh+aul rdo rje gsum lnga 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:502: 'dod pa'i dbang mo ljang gu zhal //
NK005(ca)001:503: dpag bsam lcug ma rlung gis bskyod //
NK005(ca)001:504: shar lho nub byang rim skyes so //
NK005(ca)001:506: dkar 'bar snang mdzad dge slong can //
NK005(ca)001:507: chos kyi 'khor lo glegs bam dang //
NK005(ca)001:508: mkhar gsil lhung bzed mtshan dper ldan //
NK005(ca)001:510: sngo sangs sangs rgyas byang chub ma //
NK005(ca)001:511: rdo rje lce yi rnam par bsgom //
NK005(ca)001:513: dpa' mo gser mdog cha lang 'khrol //
NK005(ca)001:515: kun bzang dmar mo rin chen 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:517: mi bzad ljang gu dung 'dzin ma //
NK005(ca)001:520: sprin chen dmar mo sprin chen 'bebs //
NK005(ca)001:522: nam mkha'i spyan ma pad+ma dkar //
NK005(ca)001:524: sangs rgyas dbyangs ma ser mo zhags //
NK005(ca)001:525: tsha skyes dbang mo pad+ma ljang //
NK005(ca)001:526: dkyil 'khor re'u mig phyogs bzhir rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:527: de bzhin gshegs mdzad kun tu 'khril //
NK005(ca)001:528: hi skyes he ru mthing ga'i sku //
NK005(ca)001:529: g.yas pa zhi la g.yon pa chags //
NK005(ca)001:530: rmongs byed zhal ni rgyab na 'byung //
NK005(ca)001:531: rdo rje kha t+w+aam dril bu 'khrol //
NK005(ca)001:532: g.yang gzhi 'jigs byed pags pa brdeb //
NK005(ca)001:533: mda' gzhu thod pa snying khrag bkang //
NK005(ca)001:534: gar gyi nyams dgu 'gying ba'i zhal //
NK005(ca)001:535: h+r+aih dkar mo mda' 'dzin ko'u r+ai ma //
NK005(ca)001:536: hi skyes tso'u r+ai dmar mo zhal //
NK005(ca)001:537: lcags kyu kha t+w+aam chos 'khor brgyad //
NK005(ca)001:538: dzih be ta ba dan kham phor dkar //
NK005(ca)001:539: dzih pra mo dmar mo phyag bzhi ma //
NK005(ca)001:545: ba dan tri sh+aul rab tu khros //
NK005(ca)001:547: g+hasma nag mo ral gri me //
NK005(ca)001:549: sme sha sngon mo thod khrag gsol //
NK005(ca)001:550: rdo rje kha t+w+aam thod pa zhags //
NK005(ca)001:553: dkar mo mtshon cha mda' gzhung dkar //
NK005(ca)001:555: ser mo kha t+w+aam dril bu 'khrol //
NK005(ca)001:557: dmar ser 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad bskor //
NK005(ca)001:559: sna tshogs ljang gu ba dan 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:561: he ru ka yi zla gam rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:563: nyi ma ser po mda' gri g.yas //
NK005(ca)001:564: gzhu pad nyi ma rdo rjes mtshan //
NK005(ca)001:566: dbang bskur dkar mo dbu rgyan 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:567: h+r+aih gser ldan ser mo rin chen sgrom //
NK005(ca)001:568: hoh rgyal mtshan dmar mo rin chen rgyal //
NK005(ca)001:570: mchod chen ljang gu rin chen snod //
NK005(ca)001:571: gtso la 'khor zhing phyogs bzhir gnas //
NK005(ca)001:572: dzah mda' 'dzin dmar ser mda' gzhu can //
NK005(ca)001:574: sngon mo kha t+w+aam ral gri 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:576: dmar ser nyi mi'i dkyil 'khor can //
NK005(ca)001:577: rdo rje ljang ser mchod sdong can //
NK005(ca)001:578: rdo rje nyi ma rin chen rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:579: h+r+aih gar dbang dmar po pad+ma 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:580: zhal gcig phyag gnyis rnam par mdzes //
NK005(ca)001:581: yang na rdo rje dril mtshan pa //
NK005(ca)001:582: nyi shu gcig dang lnga bcu gnyis //
NK005(ca)001:583: dzah rnam gzigs dkar po pad+ma 'byed //
NK005(ca)001:585: sgrol ma dmar skya ut+pala sku //
NK005(ca)001:588: hoh khro gnyer rdo rje ut+pala ljang //
NK005(ca)001:590: gtum po pad+ma rdo rje mthing //
NK005(ca)001:593: +aah pad+ma chu srin rgyal mtshan dkar //
NK005(ca)001:594: hoh pad+ma ljang gu pad+ma bsgrub //
NK005(ca)001:595: phyed phyed phyi nang re'u mig rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:596: pad+ma gar dbang chu skyes rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:597: +aah ljang ser rta mchog rta gdong ljang //
NK005(ca)001:598: ba dan gsum pa sna tshogs thugs //
NK005(ca)001:599: ral gri mda' ni bzhi par 'chang //
NK005(ca)001:600: sna tshogs pad+ma mdung rtse gsum //
NK005(ca)001:601: be con gzhu ni bzhi par 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:602: 'gying brjid gar gyi skur ldan dgyes //
NK005(ca)001:604: sna tshogs pad+ma dkar ljang g.yas //
NK005(ca)001:606: sngo ljang rdo rje sna tshogs g.yas //
NK005(ca)001:607: las bzhi rta mchog rim par sbyar //
NK005(ca)001:608: rgya gram rta yi 'khor lor rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:609: h+aum skyes dkar po rta zhal 'gugs //
NK005(ca)001:610: a skyes sngon mo gling bu 'bud //
NK005(ca)001:612: ser mo rdo rje pi wang 'dren //
NK005(ca)001:614: rnga chen dmar mo rnga ring brdungs //
NK005(ca)001:616: rdza rnga ljang gu rdo rje mtshon //
NK005(ca)001:617: zlum zhing 'khyil nas grwa la rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:618: dz+ha skyes ser po rta zhal zhags //
NK005(ca)001:620: dmar ser rdo rje me tog snod //
NK005(ca)001:621: spos snod dkar mo a skyes ma //
NK005(ca)001:622: +aah dmar skya mar me ba dan 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:625: mchod pa'i dkyil 'khor thig le rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:626: bam skyes dmar mo rta zhal lcags //
NK005(ca)001:627: h+aum skyes dkar mo la sogs gzugs //
NK005(ca)001:628: m+aa le phreng ba tram skyes sngo //
NK005(ca)001:629: g+airti dmar mo glu len h+r+aih a skyes n+airti ljang gu gar //
NK005(ca)001:630: dbang mchog rgyal po grwa la rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:631: h+aum skyes byung ba ljang gu dril //
NK005(ca)001:632: r+au skyes dkar mo me long gzungs //
NK005(ca)001:633: hi skyes ser mo dri snod ma //
NK005(ca)001:634: dzi skyes dmar mo dri bsung snod //
NK005(ca)001:635: tsi skyes ljang gu zhal zas so //
NK005(ca)001:637: dkar mo rta gdong lcags kyu shar //
NK005(ca)001:639: phag gdong nag mo zhags thogs lho //
NK005(ca)001:640: h+aum las skyes pa snying rje bdag /
NK005(ca)001:641: seng dmar thabs shes lcags sgro nub //
NK005(ca)001:642: bam las byung ba dga' ba dmar //
NK005(ca)001:643: ljang gu thal byed spyang dril byang //
NK005(ca)001:644: hohls skyes pa btang snyoms las /
NK005(ca)001:645: rig pa las skyes ye dag phyir //
NK005(ca)001:646: rdzogs chen rnal 'byor dus gcig rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:647: kun tu dmigs la rig par ldan //
NK005(ca)001:648: gti mug can la gti mug ste //
NK005(ca)001:649: zhe sdang can la zhe yang sdang //
NK005(ca)001:650: gdug pa khro gtum 'dod pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)001:651: ser sna can la ser snas bsdams //
NK005(ca)001:653: phrag dog la yang phrag dog go //
NK005(ca)001:654: 'dul phyir rigs su bsdus pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:655: bye brag rnams la bye brag ston //
NK005(ca)001:656: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK005(ca)001:657: bsam yas 'dod pa kun ster phyir //
NK005(ca)001:658: rig pa'i sprul pa rgya chen mchod //
NK005(ca)001:659: gdung ba'i glu dang mdzes pa'i gar //
NK005(ca)001:660: rol mo las kyi karmasa dbul //
NK005(ca)001:662: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:663: lha rnam par bkod pa'i le'u ste rtog pa bzhi pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:665: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku
NK005(ca)001:666: dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi
NK005(ca)001:667: dkyil 'khor thams cad yongs su mnyes par byed pa
NK005(ca)001:668: kun tu rnam par sprul pa'i rol pa chen po
NK005(ca)001:669: rol mo'i rgyan zhes bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:670: rig pa rig pa nyid la gnas //
NK005(ca)001:671: de phyir rig pa rig pa'i sprul pa ste //
NK005(ca)001:672: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pas khyab pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)001:673: spyan drangs gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK005(ca)001:674: thugs rje'i ngang chen chos skur dag pa las //
NK005(ca)001:675: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)001:676: bsnyengs pa mi mnga' stobs bcu'i shugs mnga' ba //
NK005(ca)001:677: ma 'dres sangs rgyas chos rnams rab tu rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:678: dpal chen longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)001:679: rngams pa'i zhal nas 'brug sgrog cing //
NK005(ca)001:680: seng ge'i nga ros kyang ni bskyod du med //
NK005(ca)001:681: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams zil gyis gnod mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)001:682: bcom ldan 'gro la brtse slad gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)001:683: mkha' 'gro kun dang thabs cig gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)001:684: sgyu ma gar gyi rol bas 'dren //
NK005(ca)001:685: rig pa nyid la ye shes 'jug /
NK005(ca)001:686: mthu ldan nus pa rtog pa sel //
NK005(ca)001:687: mchod pa'i rnam pa thams cad la //
NK005(ca)001:688: m+aam sa chu dang zil pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:689: grub pa bzhi yis rab brgyan pa //
NK005(ca)001:690: ting 'dzin mthu dang ngo bos grub //
NK005(ca)001:691: sangs rgyas rnams la tsan+dana spros //
NK005(ca)001:692: rdo rje can la gur gum yin //
NK005(ca)001:693: spyan ras gzigs la tsan+dana dmar //
NK005(ca)001:694: ga bur rdo rje nyi ma la //
NK005(ca)001:695: me tog kun dang bdug pa kun //
NK005(ca)001:696: de bzhin mar me thams cad dang //
NK005(ca)001:697: spos rnams thams cad ji snyed pa //
NK005(ca)001:698: rdo rje 'chang la dbul du rung //
NK005(ca)001:699: smin dang g.yo ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)001:701: rang byung bi mu ma ra shu //
NK005(ca)001:702: go ku da dang ha na'i rgyan //
NK005(ca)001:703: h+aum b+h+r+aum +aam dz+rim kham zhes pa //
NK005(ca)001:704: dbus shar lho nub byang du gnas //
NK005(ca)001:706: dag shu spel bas kha dog dril //
NK005(ca)001:707: h+r+aihls byung ba ye shes me //
NK005(ca)001:708: stong nyid rdo rje khong seng can //
NK005(ca)001:710: sangs rgyas sprin tshogs sbyin par bstim //
NK005(ca)001:711: lug ngag mthu ldan nus pa che //
NK005(ca)001:712: bgegs rnams 'joms pas mtshams kyi mchog /
NK005(ca)001:713: shangs kyi 'od zer rlung sgrom nas //
NK005(ca)001:714: 'khyil zhing spro ba gsal byed dbyangs //
NK005(ca)001:715: keng zhes rul sbal kha 'dra ba //
NK005(ca)001:716: kha ni bum pa 'bab pa ste //
NK005(ca)001:717: ga ni bse yi kha dang mtshungs //
NK005(ca)001:718: g+ha ni bum pa lta bu ste //
NK005(ca)001:719: nga ni kang ka nyid dang 'dra //
NK005(ca)001:720: tsa ni tsa sha nyid dang mtshungs //
NK005(ca)001:721: tsha ni gdugs kyi sba ba 'dra //
NK005(ca)001:722: dza ni rnga mo'i mgo bo bzhin //
NK005(ca)001:723: dz+ha ni rnga chen gzugs lta bu //
NK005(ca)001:724: ta ni sked nyag lta bu ste //
NK005(ca)001:726: da ni thi ba'i kha nyid de //
NK005(ca)001:727: d+ha ni mkha' 'gro nyid du go //
NK005(ca)001:728: na ni sbyin bdag dang 'dra ba //
NK005(ca)001:729: ta ni sdang dang 'dra ba ste //
NK005(ca)001:730: pha wang kha 'dra yi ge tha //
NK005(ca)001:731: da ni mche ba can dang mtshungs //
NK005(ca)001:732: d+ha nyid gzhu yi ngo bo nyid //
NK005(ca)001:733: na ni ma he'i kha 'dra ba //
NK005(ca)001:734: ri skegs 'gros ni pa zhes bya //
NK005(ca)001:735: pha ni khrung khrung mgo dang mtshungs //
NK005(ca)001:736: 'dam bya ba ste skye ga b+ha //
NK005(ca)001:737: ma ni spre'u'i mtshul pa'i gzugs //
NK005(ca)001:738: phug ron dur pa ya dang ra //
NK005(ca)001:739: khu byung bya rog la dang wa //
NK005(ca)001:740: sha sha ri bong zhi ba'i spyan /
NK005(ca)001:741: sa ha spyang ku 'phrog ma dang //
NK005(ca)001:742: k+sha ni srin bu'i kha lta bu //
NK005(ca)001:743: de rnams kha dang 'gros kyis dbyibs //
NK005(ca)001:744: mtshon pas phrin las rnam bzhi bsdus //
NK005(ca)001:745: a ni khyim bya'i mgo bo'i gzugs //
NK005(ca)001:747: i ni glang chen sna lta bu //
NK005(ca)001:749: +au ni rnga mo'i mgo bo bzhin //
NK005(ca)001:751: ri ni ri bong mgo bo 'dra //
NK005(ca)001:752: yi ge r+ai ni seng mgo bzhin //
NK005(ca)001:753: yi ge li ni glang chen la //
NK005(ca)001:754: l+ai ni dbang ldan zhal dang mtshungs //
NK005(ca)001:755: e ni ma he'i kha 'dra ba //
NK005(ca)001:756: ee ni rma bya'i kha dang mtshungs //
NK005(ca)001:757: o ni byi la'i kha dang mtshungs //
NK005(ca)001:758: oo ni khyim bya'i kha bzhin no //
NK005(ca)001:759: am ni chu srin mgo bo 'dra //
NK005(ca)001:760: tsheg drag ahni rta mgo bzhin //
NK005(ca)001:761: spyir na bsam yas dbyibs gsungs pa //
NK005(ca)001:762: rang bzhin nyid kyis rnam bzhir 'dus //
NK005(ca)001:763: thabs dang shes rab 'thab pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:764: ring thung gar dang lcong du 'byung //
NK005(ca)001:765: de nyid sgra yi 'byung gnas su //
NK005(ca)001:766: ha pa lngar ka sorga rta //
NK005(ca)001:767: sha ra pa dang gar ra pa //
NK005(ca)001:768: breng nge ba dang dung nge ba //
NK005(ca)001:769: pang ge de'u dang cang ka de'u //
NK005(ca)001:770: de bzhin gshegs dang rdo rje 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:771: rdo rje he ru nyi ma dang //
NK005(ca)001:772: pad+ma gar dbang rta mchog dpal //
NK005(ca)001:773: tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis 'dren pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:774: mkhun cing gdungs pa'i sgra 'byin cing //
NK005(ca)001:775: rdo rje srin po'i dur sgra 'don //
NK005(ca)001:776: rdo rje drag po gad mo che //
NK005(ca)001:778: 'brug gi sgra ltar zab pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:779: ru lu ru lu'i sgra phyung nas //
NK005(ca)001:780: glu drug blangs pas don drug rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:781: yon tan rnam bcu re rer ldan //
NK005(ca)001:782: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu yis //
NK005(ca)001:783: 'gro drug rigs dang bye brag la //
NK005(ca)001:785: sgra yi bye brag ji snyed pa //
NK005(ca)001:786: rol mo'i sgra las 'byung ba ni //
NK005(ca)001:787: snying po phyag rgya sngags rigs dang //
NK005(ca)001:788: rig pa'i sgra ni ngang gis 'byung //
NK005(ca)001:789: dzahh+aum bam hoh dung rta mdar rma ra tad ra /
NK005(ca)001:791: pra pir+ya ta ki h+aum dzah ki ni du ni h+aum drum /
NK005(ca)001:792: ta ki h+aum dzah hu lu hu lu /
NK005(ca)001:793: a la la hoh shud+d+ha sid+d+hara ri sha ya /
NK005(ca)001:799: g+he g+he ta ta ge ta g+he he na /
NK005(ca)001:803: dran a la la hoh ru ta ma ta /
NK005(ca)001:804: thal mo brdab pa'i rtag pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:816: de kong de kong de kong te badz+ra /
NK005(ca)001:821: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)001:824: dpal he ru ka'i rnga'i phyag rgya'o //
NK005(ca)001:828: dpal pad+ma thal mo brdab pa'i rnga'o //
NK005(ca)001:834: tra tra tra tra tran+ta te /
NK005(ca)001:835: da dur tra rud tra tra /
NK005(ca)001:837: ta ki h+aum dza ta ki h+aum dza /
NK005(ca)001:839: tram tram tram tram tra tra tra /
NK005(ca)001:840: myur zhing rab tu myur ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:841: ba ta ba ta tu tun ta ta pa ta /
NK005(ca)001:842: ta ta ta ba ta ba ru 'un ta ta ba ta /
NK005(ca)001:843: ta ta be ta ba he don /
NK005(ca)001:845: ba ta ba ta ba ta phata tra ta /
NK005(ca)001:846: shin tu myur ba'i rnga'i phyag rgya shes pa ste /
NK005(ca)001:847: sil snyan gyi phyag rgya shes pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:848: sil snyan don la brag cha'i sgra //
NK005(ca)001:849: rang bzhin med par gsan zhugs pa //
NK005(ca)001:850: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed cing //
NK005(ca)001:851: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)001:852: ye shes ngang du mi gnyis gcig pas na //
NK005(ca)001:853: 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang gsal chos nyid du //
NK005(ca)001:854: mi gnyis don phyir mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK005(ca)001:855: bdag la stsol cing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)001:856: glu yi phyag rgya 'di dag gis //
NK005(ca)001:857: glu yi phyag rgya gar bya'o //
NK005(ca)001:858: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK005(ca)001:859: byams dang snying rje dgra zun mi mnga' yang //
NK005(ca)001:860: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus la mi 'da' bas //
NK005(ca)001:861: mnyam nyid ngang gis khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)001:862: khros pas longs spyod mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)001:863: rdo rje 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)001:864: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang rin chen bdun //
NK005(ca)001:865: ma rmongs rmongs pa kun grol rgyal ba'i gnas //
NK005(ca)001:866: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)001:867: dga' rab mdzod cig dam tshig dam pa grub //
NK005(ca)001:868: sgyu ma nyid la sgyu ma spyod //
NK005(ca)001:869: sgyu ma chen po rigs kyi yum //
NK005(ca)001:870: sgyu mas sgyu ma dga' mdzad ma //
NK005(ca)001:871: tsan+dana dkar dmar nyi zla'i skad //
NK005(ca)001:872: pad+ma rdo rje thabs las byung //
NK005(ca)001:873: dga' dang mchog tu dga' dang bral //
NK005(ca)001:874: skyes pa lhan cig dga' ba'i ro //
NK005(ca)001:875: rang bzhin dngos po rnam gnyis kyis //
NK005(ca)001:876: myur du dngos grub skyed byed de //
NK005(ca)001:877: 'phral du yid ches byed pa yin //
NK005(ca)001:878: yid ni nang du chud pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:879: 'dod pa'i dngos grub bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)001:880: rang rdzas thig le phyir phyung nas //
NK005(ca)001:881: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' mchod //
NK005(ca)001:882: he ni bde chen las byung ba //
NK005(ca)001:883: ru ni rin chen chags dang bral //
NK005(ca)001:884: ka ni rab tu rmongs pa spangs //
NK005(ca)001:885: he ru ka sogs dgyes mchod rol //
NK005(ca)001:886: skye ba bdun pa dag pa'i zhing //
NK005(ca)001:887: zhing bcu bsgral ba bstan pa'i dgra //
NK005(ca)001:888: ngan song gsum ni snying rje'i gnas //
NK005(ca)001:890: thugs rje'i dam tshig snying rjes bzung //
NK005(ca)001:891: longs spyod phung po tshogs la rol //
NK005(ca)001:892: dag pa 'od gsal chos skur sbyor //
NK005(ca)001:894: bsod nams ye shes tshogs 'gyur ba //
NK005(ca)001:895: gsang ba'i dam tshig mi bcag phyir //
NK005(ca)001:896: dngos grub snying rje mchod pas rol //
NK005(ca)001:897: gzugs med dang ni gzugs snang ba //
NK005(ca)001:898: gzugs kyi mtha' ni rnam par rig /
NK005(ca)001:899: sgra med sgra ni brag cha'i sgra //
NK005(ca)001:900: rig stong sgra ni chos nyid gsung //
NK005(ca)001:901: dri med dri bral stong pa'i dri //
NK005(ca)001:902: rang bzhin sbyor ba sna yi yul //
NK005(ca)001:903: myong ba med pa myong ba'i ro //
NK005(ca)001:904: med par myong ba ba dud rtsi'i chu //
NK005(ca)001:905: reg med reg na bde 'jam zhing //
NK005(ca)001:906: reg pa bzhi bsdus lus kyis gnas //
NK005(ca)001:907: chos med chos te chos kyi mchog /
NK005(ca)001:909: kun tu bzang po'i spyod yul la //
NK005(ca)001:910: yum gyi b+ha ga chos kyi dbyings //
NK005(ca)001:911: dam tshig dri med yon tan drug /
NK005(ca)001:912: thugs dam bzhin du longs spyod rol //
NK005(ca)001:914: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:915: mchod pa'i sprin rnam par bkod pa'i phyag rgya'i le'u ste rtog pa lnga pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:917: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dkyil
NK005(ca)001:918: 'khor kun tu 'gro ba zhes bya ba 'di gsungs
NK005(ca)001:919: so // skal bzang bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK005(ca)001:920: mchod rten dben gnas skyed mos tshal //
NK005(ca)001:921: gtsug lag kun dga' ra ba ru //
NK005(ca)001:922: sems dpa' rdo rje dpa' bo bsgrub //
NK005(ca)001:923: dgon pa mchod rten gtsug lag khang //
NK005(ca)001:924: der ni rnam par snang mdzad bsgom //
NK005(ca)001:925: rgyal po'i pho brang pad+ma'i tshal //
NK005(ca)001:926: rdo rje nyi ma rab tu bsgom //
NK005(ca)001:929: sna tshogs mkhar ram chu bo'i 'gram //
NK005(ca)001:930: rgyal khams gzhan du rta mchog bsgrub //
NK005(ca)001:931: dur khrod lha rten ma mo'i gnas //
NK005(ca)001:932: he ru ka ni rab tu shis //
NK005(ca)001:935: skyon rnams bral zhing yon tan ldan //
NK005(ca)001:936: tshom bu rgyas pa bsgrub par shis //
NK005(ca)001:938: phun sum tshogs pa rab tu gces //
NK005(ca)001:939: mtho dman gseg ma gyo mo dang //
NK005(ca)001:940: tsh+wa sga shing dum ro lnga bral //
NK005(ca)001:941: blang brtag bzung dang sbyang ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:942: bskrad gsung sbyor bas cho ga rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:944: mdzes shing 'tshams pa rab tu shes //
NK005(ca)001:945: sems dpa'i skyil krung la gnas nas //
NK005(ca)001:946: rdo rje sems dpa'i gar byas te //
NK005(ca)001:947: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:948: bgegs rnams thams cad gzhig par bya //
NK005(ca)001:949: rdo rje pus mo gnyis bcings te //
NK005(ca)001:950: rdo rjee skyil mo krung bcas nas //
NK005(ca)001:951: bdag nyid stan la 'dug nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:952: bgegs rnams thams cad gzhig par bya //
NK005(ca)001:953: drag shul can la drag shul sbyor //
NK005(ca)001:954: zhal bzhi pa la phyag bzhi pa //
NK005(ca)001:955: zhabs bzhi pa la rmig pa bzhi //
NK005(ca)001:956: rta mgrin rgyal po bgegs rnams 'joms //
NK005(ca)001:957: pad+ma'i skyil krung bcas nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:958: lag pa pad+ma bskor ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:959: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:960: bgegs rnams thams cad gzhig par byed //
NK005(ca)001:961: rdo rje'i nyi ma g.yon brkyang bas //
NK005(ca)001:962: rgyas btab rmongs byas thal bar byas //
NK005(ca)001:963: khams gsum pa yang 'tsho bar byed //
NK005(ca)001:964: bgegs rnams thams cad gzhig par bya //
NK005(ca)001:965: he ru ka ni rdo rje'i 'gros //
NK005(ca)001:966: gdug pa thams cad spa yang bkong //
NK005(ca)001:967: rdo rje sems dpa' sgeg pa ste //
NK005(ca)001:968: dpa' la dpa' bo de bzhin gshegs //
NK005(ca)001:969: rdo rje 'dzin pa snying rje'i bdag /
NK005(ca)001:970: rgod pa 'jig rten dbang phyug mchog /
NK005(ca)001:971: rdo rje nyi ma khro bo'i nyams //
NK005(ca)001:972: rta mchog dregs pa 'jig par byed //
NK005(ca)001:973: sh+aakya thub pa mi sdug pas //
NK005(ca)001:974: ngo mtshar la ni a la la //
NK005(ca)001:975: rab tu zhi ba sangs rgyas so //
NK005(ca)001:977: ma 'phangs ral gri'i phyag rgya dang //
NK005(ca)001:978: lag pas 'phangs pa mdung thung sogs //
NK005(ca)001:979: 'phangs nas slar bzung zhags pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:980: rkang pa gyad kyi stobs 'gyed pas //
NK005(ca)001:981: rkang pa gshibs pas sa gnod cing //
NK005(ca)001:982: rkang pa bskyed pas sa mnan pa //
NK005(ca)001:983: dkyil 'khor gru bzhir mnan pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:984: brkyang bskum tshul gyis gnas gsum mnan //
NK005(ca)001:985: dbyings kyi phyag rgya shes par bya //
NK005(ca)001:986: mi lhod pa la sran gzugs dang //
NK005(ca)001:987: mnyen zhing yan lag bstan pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:988: rgya cher sa bzhi rnam par dag /
NK005(ca)001:989: lus kyi phyag rgya bde blag can //
NK005(ca)001:990: rkang pa mnan cing rmig pa mnan //
NK005(ca)001:991: mda' gzhu 'dren pa'i phyag rgya yis //
NK005(ca)001:992: khams gsum rgyal srid chen po dag /
NK005(ca)001:993: rnam par btul nas dga' bar spyod //
NK005(ca)001:994: nyung dkar gu gul rdzas dag dang //
NK005(ca)001:995: rgyal chen mnga' gsol phyogs skyong mnan //
NK005(ca)001:996: khro bcu bkod de dam sri mnan //
NK005(ca)001:997: chos rgyal mnga' gsol sgo byang gdags //
NK005(ca)001:998: bgegs dang lan chags sbyin pa dgye //
NK005(ca)001:999: sa yi ri mo bya ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1000: dur khrod thal ba'i ri mo bya //
NK005(ca)001:1001: dkyil 'khor sna tshogs dris byugs te //
NK005(ca)001:1002: me tog dri ni lha grangs mthun //
NK005(ca)001:1003: mchod sogs lha yi lhag par gnas //
NK005(ca)001:1004: sgrub pa'i bum pa lha grangs mnyam //
NK005(ca)001:1005: gang ba'i bum pa dag dang ni //
NK005(ca)001:1006: thams cad las kyi bum pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:1007: rnam par rgyal ba'i bum pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1008: sbyangs nas bsangs te gzhal yas khang //
NK005(ca)001:1009: bskyed drang bstim mchod bstod pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:1010: bsnyen pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:1011: bsgrub pa bsgrub pa chen po bzhi //
NK005(ca)001:1012: dkyil 'khor rab tu bsgrub par bya //
NK005(ca)001:1013: gtso dang 'khor gyi bsnyen pa bskyar //
NK005(ca)001:1014: sbyin sreg bya zhing las sgrib bshags //
NK005(ca)001:1015: skal ldan bu mchog la sogs pa //
NK005(ca)001:1016: rtags gdab dam tshig bsre bsnan bya //
NK005(ca)001:1017: sems bskyed sdom pa bzung ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1018: bdun po rnam dag spro ba bskyed //
NK005(ca)001:1019: sku gsung thugs su byin brlabs shing //
NK005(ca)001:1020: rdo rje'i khu tshur gnas gsum gtug /
NK005(ca)001:1021: spyi bor bdun dmigs snying mchod dbul //
NK005(ca)001:1023: rnam lnga ba ko tsam byugs te //
NK005(ca)001:1024: u dum+wa ra las byas pa //
NK005(ca)001:1025: sdig spangs bcu gnyis me tog thod //
NK005(ca)001:1026: dor te pra brtag srung skud gdags //
NK005(ca)001:1027: dag pa'i sngags kyi khyor chus bkru //
NK005(ca)001:1028: rigs lngar ku sha rmi lam brtags //
NK005(ca)001:1029: zhi ba rgyas pa dbang drag dang //
NK005(ca)001:1030: rdzas dang mchod pa'i rim pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:1031: ngan pa'i ltas la bsregs sbyangs shing //
NK005(ca)001:1032: sar ba'i rgyu las kha bsgyur te //
NK005(ca)001:1033: lnga'am nyi shu'i kha dog can //
NK005(ca)001:1034: rdo rje rgyun thag la sogs pa //
NK005(ca)001:1035: gsang ba'i sngags kyis bsgril nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:1036: mtshan ldan mdzes ma lhar gsal nas //
NK005(ca)001:1038: nam mkha' gang ba'i bde gshegs rnams //
NK005(ca)001:1039: khyed kyi 'gro don mdzad dus lags //
NK005(ca)001:1040: thig le sgra 'dis bskul nas kyang /
NK005(ca)001:1041: de rnams 'dir ni gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)001:1042: gsang ba'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang //
NK005(ca)001:1043: dkyil 'khor thig gdab shes rab can //
NK005(ca)001:1044: phyogs kun mnyam pa nyid dmigs nas //
NK005(ca)001:1045: shar lho nub byang phyogs rnams su //
NK005(ca)001:1046: thig bzhi btab pas dkyil 'khor dgu //
NK005(ca)001:1047: dkyil 'khor zlum po sangs rgyas kyi //
NK005(ca)001:1049: rdo rje can gyi zla gam dgu //
NK005(ca)001:1050: pad+ma dbang gi chu skyes brgyad //
NK005(ca)001:1051: rdo rje nyi ma rin chen dbyibs //
NK005(ca)001:1052: sna tshogs rdo rje rgya gram can //
NK005(ca)001:1053: rta yi rgyal po yang dag gnas //
NK005(ca)001:1055: ji ltar dus dang ci bde ba'i //
NK005(ca)001:1056: dkyil 'khor kun tu gnas pa dpal //
NK005(ca)001:1057: phrin las karma'i rigs yin phyir //
NK005(ca)001:1058: rta mchog phyag rgya cir yang gsal //
NK005(ca)001:1059: mtshams bzhi las bzhi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)001:1060: las bzhi'i rigs kyi rgyal po la //
NK005(ca)001:1061: lha mo bcu drug 'khor lo che //
NK005(ca)001:1062: rta babs brgyad ldan t+aa ra na //
NK005(ca)001:1063: mdzes pa'i rgyan bzhi 'debs pa'i tshul //
NK005(ca)001:1064: phyogs mtshams steng 'og mnyam gnas pas //
NK005(ca)001:1065: dur khrod brgyad kyis yongs su bskor //
NK005(ca)001:1066: ma mo brgyad dang lha chen brgyad //
NK005(ca)001:1067: zhing skyong shing dang klu chen brgyad //
NK005(ca)001:1068: sh+aakya thub mdzad mthar phyin cing //
NK005(ca)001:1069: mchod rten brgyad ni bsgom tshul mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:1070: ye shes me brgyad rab tu 'bar //
NK005(ca)001:1071: byams pa'i chu chen brgyad 'bab cing //
NK005(ca)001:1072: snying rje'i brag brgyad mdzes par brtsegs //
NK005(ca)001:1073: dga' ba'i sprin brgyad kun tu 'thibs //
NK005(ca)001:1074: btang snyoms rlung brgyad rab tu 'bud //
NK005(ca)001:1075: phyogs skyong bcu ni rab tu gnas //
NK005(ca)001:1076: rab 'bring tha ma'i tshon phye la //
NK005(ca)001:1077: sngags kyis byin brlabs pra brtags te //
NK005(ca)001:1078: rigs kyi mdog la gnas 'gyur tshon //
NK005(ca)001:1079: tshom bu dgu pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK005(ca)001:1080: rigs bsdus chen por bri ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1081: gdul bya 'dul phyir re re bzhengs //
NK005(ca)001:1082: rab gnas rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK005(ca)001:1083: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK005(ca)001:1084: 'byor ba'i longs spyod gang yin pa //
NK005(ca)001:1085: rgyan dang mtshon cha rig pas sbyar //
NK005(ca)001:1086: slob dpon zhugs nas slob ma 'jug /
NK005(ca)001:1087: gang la babs pa'i rigs kyi lha //
NK005(ca)001:1088: spyan dbye gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ltos //
NK005(ca)001:1089: rigs dang sbyar nas dbang yang rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:1090: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las //
NK005(ca)001:1091: dkyil 'khor rnal 'byor spros pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1093: // dee nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsang ba sbyin pa zhes bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:1094: lus kyi dkyil 'khor gru bzhi la //
NK005(ca)001:1095: rdo rjee mchu dang rdo rje bcas //
NK005(ca)001:1096: mtshon can po dag bsgrub pa ni //
NK005(ca)001:1097: mthu yis rab tu grub pa ste //
NK005(ca)001:1098: pad+ma'i snod kyi nang du gzhug /
NK005(ca)001:1099: chags pa chen po bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)001:1100: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK005(ca)001:1101: sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i thugs //
NK005(ca)001:1103: de yi mtshal dang khu ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1104: mtshal chen po yi bsgrub pa dag /
NK005(ca)001:1105: chags pa chen po las byung bas //
NK005(ca)001:1106: dmar chen po zhes bya bar bshad //
NK005(ca)001:1107: dmar chen po dang ga bur bcas //
NK005(ca)001:1108: tsan+dana dmar po sbyar ba dag /
NK005(ca)001:1109: tshogs kyi dbus su bzhag pa ni //
NK005(ca)001:1110: ra sa ya na kun slong bas //
NK005(ca)001:1111: rang gi lha yi sbyor ldan pas //
NK005(ca)001:1112: srin lag mthe bo'i rtse mo yis //
NK005(ca)001:1113: zhim pa'i btung ba bzhin myangs na //
NK005(ca)001:1114: rtag pa yi ni dngos grub thob //
NK005(ca)001:1116: skal ldan gsol gdab dam tshig sbyin //
NK005(ca)001:1117: de nas khrus byas dris lus byug /
NK005(ca)001:1118: ci 'byor ba yi gos dang rgyan //
NK005(ca)001:1119: sna tshogs gos dag bgos nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:1120: kha dri zhim pa'i me tog phreng //
NK005(ca)001:1121: sna tshogs skal pa bzang po can //
NK005(ca)001:1122: slob ma dal gyis dal gyis su //
NK005(ca)001:1123: gos dag bkab pa'i sbyor ba yis //
NK005(ca)001:1124: bdag gi 'byung ba bskul bar bya //
NK005(ca)001:1125: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyi zla rnams //
NK005(ca)001:1126: shar ba dag ni mthong ba yis //
NK005(ca)001:1127: sdig pa kun las grol 'gyur zhing //
NK005(ca)001:1130: chos kyi dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK005(ca)001:1131: rim dang cig char 'jug pa yis //
NK005(ca)001:1132: de nyid yang dag bsgom pa ni //
NK005(ca)001:1133: rig pa rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NK005(ca)001:1134: dngos med rtog pa'i bag chags dag /
NK005(ca)001:1135: sgyu ma me long gzugs brnyan 'dra //
NK005(ca)001:1136: sgyu mas sgyu ma stong pas na //
NK005(ca)001:1137: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin mi dmigs phyir //
NK005(ca)001:1138: chos kyi sku 'di shes par gyis //
NK005(ca)001:1139: ji ltar nam mkha' dwangs pa la //
NK005(ca)001:1140: rang bzhin med ltar rang sems zhog /
NK005(ca)001:1141: 'od gsal chos sku rtog med la //
NK005(ca)001:1142: bslad pas dri mas gos 'gyur phyir //
NK005(ca)001:1143: ma bslad bu gcig rang sar zhog /
NK005(ca)001:1144: brjid pa chen po'i khri steng na //
NK005(ca)001:1145: skal ldan chen po bzhag nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:1146: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan ba dan dang //
NK005(ca)001:1147: rol mo rnams kyis rnam brgyan nas //
NK005(ca)001:1148: bdud rtsi rnam rgyal bum pa'i chu //
NK005(ca)001:1149: rigs kyi cod pan mdzes par bcing //
NK005(ca)001:1150: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK005(ca)001:1151: gsang ba gsum gyi gnas las byung //
NK005(ca)001:1152: dbang bskur ba yi rdo rje che //
NK005(ca)001:1153: mi ldog pa yi dbang bskur ro //
NK005(ca)001:1154: sku dbang mda' gzhu gtad pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:1155: shes rab dril bu gsung gi dbang //
NK005(ca)001:1156: thugs kyi dbang du me long bstan //
NK005(ca)001:1157: yon tan yangs pa mig thur dbang //
NK005(ca)001:1158: phrin las brtul zhugs chen po'i dbang //
NK005(ca)001:1159: gdams ngag 'debs pa tshig gi dbang //
NK005(ca)001:1160: gsang ba'i mtshan rtags ming gi dbang //
NK005(ca)001:1161: nyan dang 'chad dang bsgrub pa dang //
NK005(ca)001:1162: phrin las dbang rnams rdzogs par bskur //
NK005(ca)001:1163: 'khor lo rkang par bzhag byas nas //
NK005(ca)001:1164: lag pa g.yas par dung sbyin te //
NK005(ca)001:1165: g.yon par lce ni sbyin par bya //
NK005(ca)001:1166: 'jig rten kun la thams cad du //
NK005(ca)001:1167: sems can kun la phan pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)001:1168: ji ltar sna tshogs 'dul gyur pa //
NK005(ca)001:1169: rdo rje'i 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
NK005(ca)001:1170: khro bo'i 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
NK005(ca)001:1171: nor bu'i 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
NK005(ca)001:1173: sna tshogs 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
NK005(ca)001:1174: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud rnams la //
NK005(ca)001:1175: 'khor lo rab tu bskor ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1176: bla med rnal 'byor chen po la //
NK005(ca)001:1177: ma h+aa a nu a ti la //
NK005(ca)001:1178: blo dang mthun sbyar 'khor lo bskor //
NK005(ca)001:1179: 'gro drug sems can dbugs phyung zhing //
NK005(ca)001:1180: dri ldan ye shes mnyes bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)001:1181: gang la yongs su btang dka' ba //
NK005(ca)001:1182: gang yin de ni mchog tu bshad //
NK005(ca)001:1183: gang dang gang la yid 'ong mchog /
NK005(ca)001:1184: de dang de ni bla mar dbul //
NK005(ca)001:1185: yang na shin tu khyad par can //
NK005(ca)001:1186: bla ma'i sems la dgos pa gang //
NK005(ca)001:1187: de dbul yang na zho sha dbul //
NK005(ca)001:1188: dngos po chung la mnyes pa mchog /
NK005(ca)001:1189: rdo rje sems dpa'i yon dbul ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:1190: bu mo shin tu brgyan pa'am //
NK005(ca)001:1191: de bzhin chung ma sdug pa gang //
NK005(ca)001:1192: phul nas yon gyis bslu ba yin //
NK005(ca)001:1193: sangs rgyas byang chub mchog yin no //
NK005(ca)001:1194: rdo rje rigs la bdag nyid dbul //
NK005(ca)001:1195: slar yang rin gyis bslu bar bya //
NK005(ca)001:1196: rdo rje 'dzin pa dpal sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)001:1197: 'bul ba yon gyi mchog yin no //
NK005(ca)001:1198: mu tig bzang po nor bu dang //
NK005(ca)001:1199: shin tu dkar ba'i ras zung dang //
NK005(ca)001:1200: de bzhin rta ni dkar po dag /
NK005(ca)001:1201: pad+ma can gyi yon mchog yin //
NK005(ca)001:1202: rgyal rigs longs spyod gter rnams dang //
NK005(ca)001:1203: gos dang rgyan gyi tshogs rnams dang //
NK005(ca)001:1204: de bzhin mchod pa thams cad ni //
NK005(ca)001:1205: rdo rje nyi ma'i yon yin no //
NK005(ca)001:1206: shin tu brgyan pa'i rta dag dang //
NK005(ca)001:1207: glang po shin tu brgyan pa yang //
NK005(ca)001:1208: shing rta rin chen gang ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1209: rta dag rta mchog yon yin no //
NK005(ca)001:1210: bla ma mnyes par gang byas pa //
NK005(ca)001:1211: de ni chung yang mchog yin te //
NK005(ca)001:1212: che ste rin chen ri rab tsam //
NK005(ca)001:1213: chung ste khab skud yan chad la //
NK005(ca)001:1214: bla ma mnyes pa gang 'bul ba //
NK005(ca)001:1215: dkyil 'khor dgu yi yon yin no //
NK005(ca)001:1216: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam par sbyor ba las //
NK005(ca)001:1217: dbang bskur phyag rgya'i le'u ste rtog pa bdun pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1219: // de nas thabs yod par byin gyis brlabs pa zhes bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:1220: bla med gsang zhugs skal bzang po //
NK005(ca)001:1222: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs rnams bsrung //
NK005(ca)001:1223: dus bzhir rigs drug skur bsgom zhing //
NK005(ca)001:1224: gsang sngags phreng ba ngag la 'chang //
NK005(ca)001:1225: rdzogs pa'i rim pa sgom byed pa //
NK005(ca)001:1226: sbyor lam kun las nyams pa med //
NK005(ca)001:1227: zhing dang sngags dang las skyes ma //
NK005(ca)001:1228: mtshan bzang gang yin bde ba skye //
NK005(ca)001:1229: dam tshig gsang ba kun tu bsrung //
NK005(ca)001:1230: zhing bcu'i tshogs la gnas spor cing //
NK005(ca)001:1231: 'gal ba dag la mtshon cha'i char //
NK005(ca)001:1232: phab nas bde bar gshegs la 'bul //
NK005(ca)001:1233: yum drug dam tshig la gnas phyir //
NK005(ca)001:1234: dam tshig dam pa sngags kyi sgra //
NK005(ca)001:1235: na mosh+tu sarba b+hud+d+he b+h+yah zhes pa'i phyag rgya la gnas na //
NK005(ca)001:1236: las dang mchod pa ma lus pa //
NK005(ca)001:1237: lus pa med pa thams cad 'grub //
NK005(ca)001:1238: rab byung rnams kyi grub pa kun //
NK005(ca)001:1239: chos dbyings mnyam dang mi mnyam pa //
NK005(ca)001:1240: nam mkha' dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa'i //
NK005(ca)001:1241: lan gcig brjod pas 'grub pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)001:1242: dam tshig chos kyi phyag rgya 'dis //
NK005(ca)001:1243: gang dag byas par ma gyur cig /
NK005(ca)001:1244: spel ba dag kyang ma gyur cig /
NK005(ca)001:1245: dam pa rgya chen de dag med //
NK005(ca)001:1246: ru ru spu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+ha lo tsa na sarba ar+tha s+aa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)001:1247: chos kyi phyag rgya mchog 'di ni //
NK005(ca)001:1248: sems can thams cad bya byed pa //
NK005(ca)001:1249: stobs kyis myur du bkug nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:1250: bran bzhin de ni byed du 'jug /
NK005(ca)001:1251: d+hu ba b+ha ga ta ma h+aa de bi hi ri mi ri ni sh+re ya /
NK005(ca)001:1252: chos kyi dam pa phyag rgya 'di //
NK005(ca)001:1253: 'dod pa bde ba kun sbyin pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1254: +amo t+aa re tu t+t+aa re tu re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)001:1255: chos kyi phyag rgya la gnas pa //
NK005(ca)001:1256: sangs rgyas byang chub rab bsgrub nas //
NK005(ca)001:1257: bud med gzhan lta ci zhig smos //
NK005(ca)001:1258: tram ba ba ta ta ta ta ta /
NK005(ca)001:1259: re ba thams cad kun rdzogs pa //
NK005(ca)001:1260: chos kyi phyag rgya dam pa 'di //
NK005(ca)001:1261: re ba thams cad rdzogs byed pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1262: sh+r+ai badz+ra pad+ma ba ta ba mu kha yo g+ai shwa ri hi hi hi hi hi /
NK005(ca)001:1263: chos kyi phyag rgya dam pa 'di //
NK005(ca)001:1265: 'di rnams dam tshig mchog yin te //
NK005(ca)001:1266: chos kyi phyag rgya shes pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1267: zhe sdang chen pos zhe sdang ba //
NK005(ca)001:1268: gti mug chen pos gti mug che //
NK005(ca)001:1269: nga rgyal nga rgyal dag la gnas //
NK005(ca)001:1271: de bzhin phrag dog phrag dog nyid //
NK005(ca)001:1272: khong khro rab tu gtum gdug can //
NK005(ca)001:1274: rigs kyi dam tshig chen po ni //
NK005(ca)001:1276: dam tshig rnam pa cir snang yang //
NK005(ca)001:1277: chos nyid ngang las ma yengs par //
NK005(ca)001:1278: rtsa ba yan lag mi 'da' bar //
NK005(ca)001:1279: grub pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs //
NK005(ca)001:1280: slob dpon la ni rtag tu gus //
NK005(ca)001:1281: mched la gdung zhing gsang ba thub //
NK005(ca)001:1282: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK005(ca)001:1283: rig pa nyid de skyes pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1285: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:1286: thams cad yod pa dam tshig gi le'u ste rtog pa brgyad pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1288: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis sna tshogs
NK005(ca)001:1289: rab tu gsal ba zhes bya ba 'di gsungs so
NK005(ca)001:1291: yongs grub 'dod yon lha skur gsal //
NK005(ca)001:1292: gzhan yang 'dod yon lha mor bcas //
NK005(ca)001:1293: rigs drug lha tshogs rnam par mchod //
NK005(ca)001:1295: dpral ba mgrin pa snying ga spyi //
NK005(ca)001:1296: lte ba lkog ma gsang ba ru //
NK005(ca)001:1298: lag pa gzar bu rnam gnyis kyis //
NK005(ca)001:1299: lus kyi dkyil 'khor mchod nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:1300: ye shes mes ni bag chags bsreg /
NK005(ca)001:1301: thal ba bshang lam las phyung ba //
NK005(ca)001:1302: nang gi sbyin sreg mchod pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1303: phrin las 'khor lo bsgom pa ni //
NK005(ca)001:1304: dge dang mi dge lung ma bstan //
NK005(ca)001:1305: lus ngag spyod pa rnam dag pa //
NK005(ca)001:1306: 'od gsal chos sku bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)001:1307: phrin las sgrib dag mchod pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1308: nyams chag skong ba'i 'khor lo bskor ba ni //
NK005(ca)001:1309: rigs drug lha yi thugs ka ru //
NK005(ca)001:1310: rta mchog 'khor lo nyid bsgoms nas //
NK005(ca)001:1311: de la dbang lnga bskur byas na //
NK005(ca)001:1312: nyams pa dag par byed pa ste //
NK005(ca)001:1313: dam tshig nyams pa dbang bskur mchod pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1314: rtog pa 'khrul pa'i 'khor lo bsgom pa ni //
NK005(ca)001:1315: rnam rtog shas che'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1316: khrus kyi 'khor lo bsgom pa ste //
NK005(ca)001:1317: rigs drug mdun du 'khor lo drug /
NK005(ca)001:1318: bum pa drug ni rdzas dang ldan //
NK005(ca)001:1319: lha bsgoms sngags ni grangs rdzogs nas //
NK005(ca)001:1321: le lo gzhom pa'i 'khor lo ni //
NK005(ca)001:1322: le lo shas che'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1323: rgyun chad med pa thun bzhi ru //
NK005(ca)001:1324: lha yi 'khor lo spro bsdu bsgom //
NK005(ca)001:1325: ldang ba sprul pa'i sku yin te //
NK005(ca)001:1326: rmi lam longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)001:1327: gnyid log chos skur bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)001:1329: yid skyo gsang ba'i 'khor lo ni //
NK005(ca)001:1330: yid ni skyo ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1331: rgyun du lha yi rnal 'byor goms //
NK005(ca)001:1332: dang po'i las kyi rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1333: grangs dus mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa skyol //
NK005(ca)001:1334: yid skyo bseng ba'i mchod pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1335: mi brtan pa yi 'khor lo ni //
NK005(ca)001:1336: mtshan ma thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1337: mtshan ma brtan par bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)001:1338: brtan pa thob pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1339: brtan pa yang dag sbyor ba'i 'khor lo ni //
NK005(ca)001:1340: mtshan thob mngon shes skyes pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1341: mchog gi dngos grub yang dag ye shes bsgom //
NK005(ca)001:1342: yang dag dbang bar bsgom pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1343: 'di ltar gnas pa'i rnal 'byor gang yin pa //
NK005(ca)001:1344: rab ni sku lnga lhun grub thob //
NK005(ca)001:1346: tha ma lha mi'i mtshan rdzogs pa //
NK005(ca)001:1349: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis 'di gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:1350: rang gi lha yi rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1351: gdong rgyan gon te bsgrub pa ni //
NK005(ca)001:1352: gsang sngags brjod na 'grub pa ste //
NK005(ca)001:1353: t+w+aam ki h+aum dzah lhar gsal nyin re de brjod na //
NK005(ca)001:1354: rdo rje sems dpa'i dngos grub thob //
NK005(ca)001:1355: rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i dngos grub ni //
NK005(ca)001:1356: bde mchog ma yi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK005(ca)001:1357: ts+tshir bzlas bsgrub bya'i snying gcod 'gyur //
NK005(ca)001:1359: tsi gis bsgrub bya'i snying bcad nas //
NK005(ca)001:1360: ts+tshi dam ts+tshi dam h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)001:1361: bzlas na bsgrub bya gang yin pa //
NK005(ca)001:1362: ma shi'i bar du 'gugs par byed //
NK005(ca)001:1363: khrag 'thung chen po sme sha ni //
NK005(ca)001:1364: bsgoms te 'di nyid ngag tu brjod //
NK005(ca)001:1367: byin rlabs mngon sum lam mkhas pa //
NK005(ca)001:1368: rnal 'byor can gyi sgrub pa pos //
NK005(ca)001:1370: bzlas na nyes pa kun las grol //
NK005(ca)001:1371: rigs drug bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)001:1372: dge ba'i brtul zhugs byas nas ni //
NK005(ca)001:1373: swo bsdams lce rtse rkan gtad nas //
NK005(ca)001:1375: rdo rje'i bzlas pa de yis ni //
NK005(ca)001:1376: rgyal ba kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK005(ca)001:1377: thig le stong pa yi ge gsum //
NK005(ca)001:1378: kun dang mthun pa de nyid thob //
NK005(ca)001:1379: bzhengs bzhugs spyod lam thams cad du //
NK005(ca)001:1380: h+aum las byung ba'i he ru ka /
NK005(ca)001:1381: mthing nag zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
NK005(ca)001:1382: stong nyid rdo rje thabs kyi mda' //
NK005(ca)001:1383: sku yi kha t+w+aam shes rab gzhu //
NK005(ca)001:1384: rang gi phyag tu rnam par 'dzin //
NK005(ca)001:1385: ko'u r+ai la sogs ma mo brgyad //
NK005(ca)001:1386: zla gam dgu pa'i dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK005(ca)001:1387: 'bru brgyad bsnyen pa ngag tu brjod //
NK005(ca)001:1388: sngags 'dis yongs rdzogs chu bur ba //
NK005(ca)001:1389: +amo badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka ma d+ha sarba dush+tana /
NK005(ca)001:1390: skur gsal rnal 'byor de nyid la //
NK005(ca)001:1391: bka' nyan go bgos bcings pa na //
NK005(ca)001:1392: bgegs kyi sbyor ba kun dang bral //
NK005(ca)001:1393: kam las rdo rje go khrab ste //
NK005(ca)001:1394: ham zhes rdo rje rgyun thag bsdams //
NK005(ca)001:1395: las rin chen h+aum rin chen //
NK005(ca)001:1396: thag gnyis mdzub gu la bcing ngo //
NK005(ca)001:1397: rat+na m+aa le a b+hi shiny+tsa //
NK005(ca)001:1398: rin chen phreng bas bcing ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1400: dar dpyangs dkar po g.yas su 'phur //
NK005(ca)001:1402: dar dbyangs dmar po g.yon du 'phur ba'o //
NK005(ca)001:1403: dur khrod thod pa'i khang pa ru //
NK005(ca)001:1404: h+aum yig rdo rje yongs gyur pas //
NK005(ca)001:1405: sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum zhes pa //
NK005(ca)001:1407: dur dmar ba dan kha t+w+aam bcas /
NK005(ca)001:1408: +amo badz+ra he ru ka k+sha pa ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)001:1409: gsang sngags 'di la gnas gyur na //
NK005(ca)001:1410: da lta nyid du sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1412: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las //
NK005(ca)001:1413: las sna tshogs par las kyi phreng ba'i le'u ste rtog pa dgu pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1415: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi yon
NK005(ca)001:1416: tan yongs su brjod pa zhes bya ba 'di gsungs
NK005(ca)001:1418: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam nyid mchog gi chos nyid can //
NK005(ca)001:1419: thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:1420: yon tan mtha' yas dngos grub thams cad sbyin mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)001:1421: dri med mi g.yo mnyam nyid dam pa'i mchog chos can //
NK005(ca)001:1422: yon tan shin tu phra ba'i cha la'ang tshad med de //
NK005(ca)001:1423: dpe ni nam mkha' la yang kun tu yod pa min //
NK005(ca)001:1424: dngos grub mtha' yas mnyam med dpe dang bral ba'i rnams //
NK005(ca)001:1425: sems can khams la dngos grub mchog rnams nges par stsol //
NK005(ca)001:1426: rtag tu dri ma med pa thugs rje'i shugs las byung //
NK005(ca)001:1427: smon lam 'grub pa 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid can //
NK005(ca)001:1428: 'gro ba'i don grub rab tu brtson pa mtha' yas pa //
NK005(ca)001:1429: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang //
NK005(ca)001:1430: tshad med tshad dang bral ba shin tu rdzogs pa yi //
NK005(ca)001:1431: bde bar gshegs pa'i gong 'phang dam pa shin tu mnyes gyur kyang //
NK005(ca)001:1432: khams gsum rnams la dngos grub mchog rtsol mdzad pa yi //
NK005(ca)001:1433: thugs rje'i spyod pa mi g.yo 'gag par yang mi 'gyur //
NK005(ca)001:1434: e ma ho shin tu bzang po'i chos nyid mchog dang ldan //
NK005(ca)001:1435: mchog sbyin rnams kyi nang na go 'phang mchog mnyes pas //
NK005(ca)001:1436: khams gsum kun la dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad pa yi //
NK005(ca)001:1437: mgon po dus gsum sgrib pa med par rab mkhyen pa //
NK005(ca)001:1438: dam tshig mchog gsum dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)001:1440: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis shin
NK005(ca)001:1441: tu gdug pa 'dul ba'i tshogs rnams la yon tan
NK005(ca)001:1443: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK005(ca)001:1444: rgod dang gshe dang rngams pa'i nga ro dang //
NK005(ca)001:1445: snying rje rngam dang ngo mtshar chen po dang /
NK005(ca)001:1446: sku yi dngos po shin tu 'gyur ba'i gar //
NK005(ca)001:1447: dur khrod rus pa'i rgyan rnams rab tu mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:1448: theg mchog glang chen ko ba brjid dang ldan //
NK005(ca)001:1449: thabs mkhas zhing chen pags pa mdzes pa'i rgyan //
NK005(ca)001:1450: 'jo sgeg stag gis pags pa chos nyid rgyan //
NK005(ca)001:1451: rak+ta thal chen zhag gis mi srun dbang du sdud //
NK005(ca)001:1452: bdud dang srin po tshar gcod r+au tra sgrol //
NK005(ca)001:1453: dpa' rtags mtshon cha thabs kyi ye shes me //
NK005(ca)001:1454: bdud kyi bdud 'joms bdud dpung thal bar rlog /
NK005(ca)001:1455: drag po drag chen drag rgyal he ru ka /
NK005(ca)001:1456: mtshan dpes rgyan ldan 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)001:1457: sku yi gar mdzad gsang sgor 'gro ba 'jug /
NK005(ca)001:1458: tug chom 'brug sgra stong khams bgegs la sgrogs //
NK005(ca)001:1459: gad rgyangs gad mos gsang ba'i bshugs glu len //
NK005(ca)001:1460: rtag chad mu stegs 'gog pa nyan thos bu //
NK005(ca)001:1461: dman pa'i theg pa log lta 'byung po 'dul //
NK005(ca)001:1462: seng ge'i nga ros gcan gzan gdug pa 'dul //
NK005(ca)001:1463: tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis skal ldan rnal 'byor skyong //
NK005(ca)001:1464: chos 'chad log lta tshar gcod bdud dregs 'dul //
NK005(ca)001:1465: ngan song stongs mdzad thar pa'i lam la 'god //
NK005(ca)001:1466: thugs rjes 'dren pa snying rje'i rgyun thag can //
NK005(ca)001:1467: smon 'jug sems lnga bskyed cing nyon mongs 'dul //
NK005(ca)001:1468: zhi des byams pa'i gsang ba kun la sgrogs //
NK005(ca)001:1469: 'dul sprul ma nges nges pa'i skur ston cing //
NK005(ca)001:1470: ngo mtshar gzugs snang khang stong nam mkha'i 'ja' //
NK005(ca)001:1471: sems can don mdzad 'dul sgo nyon mongs zhi //
NK005(ca)001:1472: rig pa'i rgyal po bla med he ru ka /
NK005(ca)001:1473: rig 'dzin rnal 'byor dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad //
NK005(ca)001:1474: rnam dag sku lnga 'jigs pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK005(ca)001:1475: sha dang khrag med stong pa ye shes sku //
NK005(ca)001:1476: gdos bcas dug 'joms dpa' bo 'jigs pa bral //
NK005(ca)001:1477: sku gsum lhun grub brdal ba thig le che //
NK005(ca)001:1478: snang stong dbyer med shes rab thabs ldan sku //
NK005(ca)001:1479: 'khor dang mya ngan 'das pa rdzogs par rol //
NK005(ca)001:1480: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:1481: yon tan yongs su brjod pa'i le'u ste rtog pa bcu pa'o //
NK005(ca)001:1483: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa sras sangs rgyas byang chub skal ldan ma dang /
NK005(ca)001:1495: sangs rgyas byang chub ma dang /
NK005(ca)001:1509: sna tshogs ba dan 'dzin ma dang /
NK005(ca)001:1522: gtum pa'i dbang phyug ma dang /
NK005(ca)001:1526: sna tshogs pad+ma rgya gram ma dang /
NK005(ca)001:1527: sna tshogs rdo rje ma dang /
NK005(ca)001:1548: gzhan yang dpa' bo thams cad dang /
NK005(ca)001:1551: byang chub sems dpa'i rigs su gyur pa thams cad dang //
NK005(ca)001:1552: gsang ba'i rigs su gyur pa thams cad kyis mnyes pa chen po'i mchod pas mchod do //
NK005(ca)001:1553: rtog pa'i rgyal po nyid la rjes su yi rang bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)001:1563: spro ba de nyid dbyer med par gyur te /
NK005(ca)001:1565: lam spros pa'i rgyud du ston to //
NK005(ca)001:1566: 'bras bu yongs su 'dus pa'i rgyud du ston to //
NK005(ca)001:1567: mang du bskyed pa'i rgyud du bstan to //
NK005(ca)001:1568: nyung ngu sdud pa'i rgyud du bstan to //
NK005(ca)001:1569: yongs su 'dus pa rtsa bar bstan to //
NK005(ca)001:1570: yongs su bkod pa bshad par bstan to //
NK005(ca)001:1571: lkog tu gyur par ston pa kha skong bstan to //
NK005(ca)001:1572: mdud pa dgrol bar dka' ba gcod pa bstan to //
NK005(ca)001:1573: des de bzhin du gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:1574: de nas de bzhin du mkhyen to //
NK005(ca)001:1575: de rnams de bzhin du yi rang bar gyur to //
NK005(ca)001:1577: de nyid de bzhin du gyur to //
NK005(ca)001:1578: de nyid de bzhin sdud do //
NK005(ca)001:1579: de nyid de bzhin bsdus nas de bzhin du gsungs so //
NK005(ca)001:1585: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK005(ca)001:1586: yongs su bkod pa'i rtog pa la rjes su yi
NK005(ca)001:1587: rang zhing bstan pa gtan pa'i le'u ste rtog pa
NK005(ca)001:1589: sdud pa'i rgyud dam pa gsang chen gyi rtog pa /
NK005(ca)001:1590: sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba zhes bya ba /
NK005(ca)001:1592: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku 'dus pa
NK005(ca)001:1593: chen po'i rang bzhin sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi rgyud
NK005(ca)001:1594: rdzogs so // rgya gar gyi pan+di ta sangs rgyas gsang ba dang /
NK005(ca)001:1595: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba 'brog mi dpal gyi ye
NK005(ca)001:1596: shes kyis bal yul du bsgyur cing zhus te gtan
